[normal]ir
[normal] 
[normal]UK Minerals Yearbook
[normal].  This allows the relative importance of the differen
[normal]t mineral sectors to be compared over time.  
[normal]Data for 20
[normal]10 and 2011 are shown in Table 2
[normal]. In addition, t
[normal]he value, in constant prices, of the principal mineral sectors from 1970 to 2011 is shown in
[normal] Figure 1
[normal], and clearly portrays
[normal] the
[normal]ir relative
[normal] fortunes
[normal].
